  "title": "Crispy Vietnamese Chicken Liver Stir Fry",
  "description": "A briny and silky Vietnamese dish featuring chicken liver and ferment-kimchi, made in a wok and friendly to nut-free diets.",
  "cuisine": "Vietnamese",
